    Greatest Hits (Bruce Springsteen album)
[______________________________________________]
Greatest Hits is Bruce Springsteen's first compilation album, released February 27, 1995 on Columbia Records.
It is a collection of some of Springsteen's hit singles and popular album tracks
through the years and four extra numbers at the end, mostly recorded with the E Street Band in 1995.
The latter constituted Springsteen's first (albeit very partial) release with his backing band since the late 1980s.
Some of the songs are shorter versions of the original album releases.
